THIS PROGRAM IS CURRENTLY UNDER A DEVELOPMENT FREEZE.

============
Taxi Booking
============

A. About
This program helps one to easily book taxis.
It is written fully in Python.
Modules Used:
	- Tkinter (GUI)
	- MySQL connector (to connect to MySQL database)
	- platform (System information)
	- random (random number generator for booking ID)

B. Running the program

	1. Open 'taxi' folder in the command line: 
		cd <path-to-folder>				# cd changes current directory
	2. Enter:
		python3 home.py					# runs .py file
	The program will open in a new window.
	
	DO NOT CLOSE THE COMMAND LINE WINDOW WHILE THE PROGRAM IS RUNNING. THE PROGRAM WILL TERMINATE IF DONE SO.

C. Compatibility
This application is cross-platform; however, the host system must have the following:
	1. Python 3.10 or greater.
	2. MySQL connector (mysql.connector)
	3. Tkinter
	
To install the above module(s),
1. Windows
	a. MySQL connector
		C:/> pip install mysql.connector
	b. Tkinter
		Tkinter is installed by default in default Python distribution (msstore)

2. Linux
	a. MySQL connector
		$ pip install mysql.connector
	b. Tkinter
		> Ubuntu/Debian and related:
		
		$ sudo apt install tk
		
D. MySQL database configuration

create database taxi;
create table taxi_bkgs(bkgid int primary key,start varchar(50),end varchar(50),jdate date,jtime time,taxitype varchar);
create table bus_bkgs(bkgid int primary key,start varchar(50),end varchar(50),jdate date,jtime time,bustype varchar(50));
create table users(uuid varchar(5) primary key,uname varchar(50),passwd varchar(50));

MySQL table format:
taxi_bkgs
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field    | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| bkgid    | int         | NO   | PRI | NULL    |       |
| start    | varchar(50) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| end      | varchar(50) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| jdate    | date        | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| jtime    | time        | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| taxitype | varchar(50) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
6 rows in set (0.02 sec)

bus_bkgs
+---------+-------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
